'''太陽高原'''（{{lang-la|'''Solis Planum'''}}）是位於火星的火山高原，位於另一個火山高原[[塔爾西斯|塔爾西斯]]的東南方，橫跨[[凤凰湖区|凤凰湖区]]、[[科普剌塔斯区|科普剌塔斯区]]與[[陶马斯区|陶马斯区]]。該區域的直徑約1811.23公里，中心座標26.4 S, 270.33 E。太陽高原的名稱來自火星的[[火星反照率特徵列表|古典反照率特徵]]，並於1973年正式命名<ref>[https://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/5625;jsessionid=95B57164B079C7B4E699ED9E5D8C73D5 Solis Planum, Gazetteer of Planetary Nomenclature]</ref>。

太陽高原是火星上許多大規模沙塵暴的源頭<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lpi.usra.edu/meetings/lpsc1980/pdf/1273.pdf |title=GEOLOGICAL CONSTRAINTS FOR THE SOLIS PLANUM "OASIS" ON MARS |accessdate=2017-02-03 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303194046/http://www.lpi.usra.edu/meetings/lpsc1980/pdf/1273.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並且該區域表面以下淺層區域有明顯較多的冰與水存在<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://science.sciencemag.org/content/297/5578/78 |title=Maps of Subsurface Hydrogen from the High Energy Neutron Detector, Mars Odyssey |accessdate=2017-02-03 |archive-date=2018-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180604192801/http://science.sciencemag.org/content/297/5578/78 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://science.sciencemag.org/content/300/5628/2081 |title=CO2 Snow Depth and Subsurface Water-Ice Abundance in the Northern Hemisphere of Mars |accessdate=2017-02-03 |archive-date=2018-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180603135437/http://science.sciencemag.org/content/300/5628/2081 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
